{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't do your leaving certificate, or the HSC, which it's called now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as a result of that, you could only get a job as a tradesman, as a-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you couldn't study, you couldn't go to university after that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- this was really very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I really was very good at languages, obviously, because I'd spoken all those languages before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'd spoken French, went to a French school, Hungarian, Romanian, Polish, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was my forte.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to go-- so I said to my father that I don't really want to go to this high school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, who is the Minister for Education?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Heffron.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he said, get me an appointment with the Minister for Education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the minister-- the office was in, in Bligh Street, in the city, those old buildings which are still there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was this huge office there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this man was sitting behind a desk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came in, and he said, yes?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, my father would like me to go to a proper high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Heffron was so flabbergasted that this little kid came and spoke to him directly, that he put me into Randwick Boys' High School.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise I think my career would have been curtailed somewhat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I think that's a reflection of what sort of man my father was, that he did that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you know, a little migrant child, going to see the Minister for Education, not-- not someone underneath.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I do not even know how I managed to get an appointment, because my father didn't speak English enough.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we went straight to the top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Heffron very well.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
